<L>__{exterior commerce street day}
<A>__{a stoop shouldered little man in his late 60s, harry trumbo shambles along the street, headed for mabel's diner. there's a sadness about harry, the world weary melancholy of a man who has little to smile about because he has little to care about. after a couple of steps, he's met up by doc ben lardner, a vigorous man in his 50s. he comes up behind harry and claps him on the back.}
